# Olive — LLM semantic analysis keys
# Copy this file to .env and fill in ONE of the keys below.
# The gateway works without any key (deterministic detection only).
# With a key, the LLM toggle in the dashboard activates semantic analysis.

# Option A: Anthropic (paid) — https://console.anthropic.com
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Option B: Groq (free tier) — https://console.groq.com
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
